    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045240/extras/d1d4e442d880ce81e999cd284b874ef6.poster.avif?t=1732903687\" width=600 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045240/extras/d1d4e442d880ce81e999cd284b874ef6.webm?t=1732903687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045240/extras/d1d4e442d880ce81e999cd284b874ef6.mp4?t=1732903687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045240/extras/6199a81e3dc29bafeb2e1e127402f441.avif?t=1732903687\" width=640 height=85 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >让炸弹人再次伟大</h2><br>经典再现！在《炸弹人》的重生版中，您现在可以从 4 个角色中选择一个，<strong>爆破</strong><strong>最后</strong>的敌人并生存下来。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >机械</h2><br>与经典的《炸弹人》一样，游戏的玩法包括战略性地放置炸弹，炸弹在一定时间后会向多个方向爆炸，从而摧毁障碍物和其他玩家。玩家可以拾取各种强化道具，从而获得更大的爆炸威力、更快的移动速度或一次放置更多炸弹的能力。如果玩家被炸弹（包括自己的炸弹）爆炸卷入，就会被炸死，这就要求玩家谨慎放置炸弹。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045240/extras/1fe260892cdfc28ee11a86205fda6ff4.poster.avif?t=1732903687\" width=650 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045240/extras/1fe260892cdfc28ee11a86205fda6ff4.webm?t=1732903687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045240/extras/1fe260892cdfc28ee11a86205fda6ff4.mp4?t=1732903687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与经典炸弹人的区别</h2><br>您可以从忍者、变种人、昆克斯和 Zlorp 这 4 个角色中选择一个。 每个角色都有特定的终极魔法--&quot;超速&quot;、&quot;不朽之盾&quot;、&quot;时间减缓 &quot;和 &quot;隐形&quot;。 但有一个例外--变种人也有一个 <strong>DASH</strong> 可以推动他前进，冷却时间为 3 秒。此外，变种人不受速度加成的影响，移动速度总是很慢。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045240/extras/a54fe094b23606d59af552d5c7ae0b08.poster.avif?t=1732903687\" width=650 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045240/extras/a54fe094b23606d59af552d5c7ae0b08.webm?t=1732903687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045240/extras/a54fe094b23606d59af552d5c7ae0b08.mp4?t=1732903687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><br>- 2-8 人在线 PvP<br>- 3 种摄像机：经典炸弹人、第一人称和第三人称相机<br>- 4 个字符供选择<br>- 能改变胜负的 4 个终极技能<br>- 与受邀朋友一起创建派对<br>- 与陌生人一起参加随机派对<br>- 地图上的一些东西可以被摧毁<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >演示版的局限性</h2>- 只有经典炸弹人相机（没有第一人称和第三人称相机）<br>- 只能扮演一个角色（忍者<br>- 只玩一张地图<br>- 无排行榜",
